<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Mysterious ancient armor -->
  <RI_BlindBox_Armor.label>神秘的甲胄</RI_BlindBox_Armor.label>
  <!-- EN: A rusted armor that is unclear needs to be studied on a research table in order to discover what it actually is. -->
  <RI_BlindBox_Armor.description>一件锈迹斑斑的甲胄，需要在研究台上经过研究，才能发现这到底是什么。</RI_BlindBox_Armor.description>
  <!-- EN: With Qi, you slowly opened the shell of this fragile relic, revealing its original appearance. -->
  <RI_BlindBox_Armor.comps.CompBlindBoxUsing.completedLetterText>你以灵气慢慢揭开了这件脆弱残宝的外壳，露出了其原本面貌。</RI_BlindBox_Armor.comps.CompBlindBoxUsing.completedLetterText>
  <!-- EN: Expose the relic -->
  <RI_BlindBox_Armor.comps.CompBlindBoxUsing.completedLetterTitle>揭露残宝</RI_BlindBox_Armor.comps.CompBlindBoxUsing.completedLetterTitle>
  
  <!-- EN: Unknown storage bag -->
  <RI_BlindBox_Bag.label>他人的储物袋</RI_BlindBox_Bag.label>
  <!-- EN: One came from someone else's storage bag, which could have contained something. -->
  <RI_BlindBox_Bag.description>一件储物袋，并未开启。</RI_BlindBox_Bag.description>
  <!-- EN: You injected Qi into the bag and forced it open, which turned it into rags and ashes. -->
  <RI_BlindBox_Bag.comps.CompBlindBoxUsing.completedLetterText>你以灵气强行打开了储物袋，储物袋成为了碎布，灰飞烟灭了，但里面储存的物品掉了出来。</RI_BlindBox_Bag.comps.CompBlindBoxUsing.completedLetterText>
  <!-- EN: Open the storage bag -->
  <RI_BlindBox_Bag.comps.CompBlindBoxUsing.completedLetterTitle>打开储物袋</RI_BlindBox_Bag.comps.CompBlindBoxUsing.completedLetterTitle>
  
